OL,3,CHare coursers fined after being
OL,4,Cspotted by police helicopter
OL,6,FWatch: Footage from the police
OL,7,Fhelicopter shows the men trying to
OL,8,Fevade arrest.
OL,10,FThree men have been fined after they
OL,11,Fwere caught hare coursing near
OL,12,FWinchester.
OL,14,FHampshire Police was called to the A34
OL,15,Fnear Bullington Cross in November
OL,16,F2024, following calls from the public
OL,17,Fthat people were on nearby farmland.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
