OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778526672
OL,3,CHare coursers fined after being
OL,4,Cspotted by police helicopter
OL,6,FThe decision was made to deploy the
OL,7,Fpolice helicopter, and when it arrived
OL,8,Fat the scene, three men and two dogs
OL,9,Fwere spotted in the nearby fields.
OL,11,FOfficers then moved in, tracking down
OL,12,Fthe men with the help of the eyes from
OL,13,Fthe sky.
OL,15,F23-year-old George Smith of Lyne Road
OL,16,Fin Virginia Water, Surrey, 46-year-old
OL,17,FGeorge Mark Smith of Lyne Road in
OL,18,FVirginia Water, and 48-year-old Frank
OL,19,FWickens of Monks Hill in Emsworth,
OL,20,Fwere all stopped at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778526672
OL,3,CHare coursers fined after being
OL,4,Cspotted by police helicopter
OL,6,FAll three were charged with trespass
OL,7,Fwith intent to search for or to pursue
OL,8,Fhares with dogs under Section 63 of
OL,9,Fthe Police, Crime and Sentencing Act
OL,10,F2022.
OL,12,FThey denied the offences, however were
OL,13,Ffound guilty by Magistrates in
OL,14,FAldershot on 1 May this year.
OL,16,FThey were all fined #520 each, and
OL,17,Feach ordered to pay #215 in court
OL,18,Fcosts and a #208 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
